      • move

        public void move()
        Called when move button is pressed. Moves photo to selected album unless the photo would be a duplicate in the other album. Deletes photo from this album.

      • copy

        public void copy()
        Copies photo from this album to selected album unless it is a duplicate in the selected album. Does not delete photo from current album.
